Inside the Co-Cathedral of St. John in Valletta, Malta 
Camera NIKON D300S Aperture f/4 Exposure Time 1/80 
Malta is a really interesting place. It has elements of many different cultures including Italian, Arab and English, yet it is uniquely its own.
